
======================================================================
PASTE-001 Pastebin download [CRITICAL]
======================================================================

Category:
  Malicious Code  (detector: rules)

Description:
  Downloading from paste sites is a common malware technique. Used
  in 2018 xeactor attack via ptpb.pw

Recommendation:
  Never download code from paste sites - this is a major red flag

CWE: CWE-506

Real-World Context:
  The 2018 xeactor attacker used ptpb.pw (a pastebin clone) to host
  malicious scripts. The scripts ~x and ~u were downloaded and
  executed, creating systemd timers for persistence.

Detection Patterns:
  - pastebin\.com
  - paste\.ee
  - ptpb\.pw
  - ix\.io
  - hastebin

======================================================================
